soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.data.provider

Interface IMethodSummaryProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EagerSummaryProvider, LazySummaryProvider, MemorySummaryProvider, MergingSummaryProvider, XMLSummaryProvider

    public interface IMethodSummaryProvider
    Common interface for all classes that can provide method summaries

    Steven Arzt

      • getMethodFlows

        default ClassMethodSummaries getMethodFlows(soot.SootClass sootClass,
                                            String methodSubSignature)
        Gets the data flows inside the given method for the given class. The different overloads are functionally equivalent, but may use the different types in order to be faster
        Parameters:
        sootClass - The class containing the method. If two classes B and C inherit from some class A, methods in A can either be evaluated in the context of B or C.
        methodSubSignature - The signature of the method for which to get the flow summaries.
        Returns:
        The flow summaries for the given method in the given class

      • getMethodFlows

        ClassMethodSummaries getMethodFlows(String className,
                                    String methodSignature)
        Gets the data flows inside the given method for the given class. The different overloads are functionally equivalent, but may use the different types in order to be faster
        Parameters:
        sootClass - The class containing the method. If two classes B and C inherit from some class A, methods in A can either be evaluated in the context of B or C.
        methodSignature - The signature of the method for which to get the flow summaries.
        Returns:
        The flow summaries for the given method in the given class
